<subSubSection pageId="26" pageNumber="25" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="26.[192,896,866,954]" box="[192,896,866,890]" pageId="26" pageNumber="25">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,302,866,890]" pageId="26" pageNumber="25">Ecology</emphasis>
. Lowland. Habitat unknown; probably riparian.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="26.[192,896,866,954]" box="[192,581,929,954]" pageId="26" pageNumber="25">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,297,929,953]" pageId="26" pageNumber="25">Biology</emphasis>
. Seasonality: January.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="26.[192,1440,993,1146]" pageId="26" pageNumber="25">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,416,993,1018]" pageId="26" pageNumber="25">Dispersal power</emphasis>
. Macropterous, probably capable of flight. Moderate runner. Vagility likely favoured by flight capacity.
</paragraph>
